HB 688 Original 2026 Regular Session Orgeron
Abstract: Adds Atlantic tarpon to the definition of saltwater game fish.
Present law provides definitions for freshwater and saltwater game fish.
Proposed law retains present law and adds Atlantic tarpon to the definition of saltwater game
fish.
Proposed law updates the names of saltwater game fish provided for in present law.
Effective upon signature of governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
(Amends R.S. 56:8(70)(b))
